substep.action:
Invoke the code-verify skill with:
- gate = "I-per-slice"
- slice_id = {{current_slice.id}}
- commit_sha = {{commit_sha}}
- worktree_path = {{worktree_path}}
- plan_path = {{plan_path}}
- bundle_dir = {{bundle_dir}}
- ticket_alias = {{ticket_alias}}
- ticket_slug = {{ticket_slug}}
- primary_tag = {{primary_tag}}

code-verify dispatches codesmith-validator with the per-gate
angle set; renders findings via
render-verification-report.py; returns the verdict.
